    "improvements_made": "Added missing associative entities (PRODUCT_BOM, PURCHASE_ORDER_LINE, PRODUCTION_PLAN_LINE) to correctly model many‑to‑many relationships and capture quantities. Split inventory into a generic entity with item_type to handle both raw materials and finished products. Enriched attributes with identifiers, timestamps, status fields, contact details, and quantitative controls (reorder point, safety stock). Clarified cardinalities and relationship directions, introduced foreign‑key attributes, and expanded financial_record to cover both sales and purchases. Overall model now fully supports recipe management, procurement, production planning, stock control, delivery, and accounting requirements of a pizza shop."
